'''Ghost'''是用[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]编写的博客平台，基于[[MIT许可证|MIT许可证]]开放源代码。Ghost的设计主旨是简化个人网站发布以及网上出版的过程。

Ghost是一款个人博客系统，它使用[[Node.js|Node.js]]语言和MySQL数据库开发，同时支持[[MySQL|MySQL]]、[[MariaDB|MariaDB]]、[[SQLite|SQLite]]和[[PostgreSQL|PostgreSQL]]。用户可以在支持[[Node.js|Node.js]]的服务器上使用自己的博客。

Ghost官方支持版，同时有爱好者开发的第三方中文汉化版，如Ghost的中文汉化版。Ghost提供开发插件的API和可以定制的Handlebars主题模板样式。

== 历史 ==

2012年11月，前[[WordPress|WordPress]] UI首席设计师<ref>{{cite web|title=John O'Nolan appointed Deputy Lead for the WordPress UI team|url=http://make.wordpress.org/ui/2010/05/20/yo-having-been-repeatedly-impressed-by/|publisher=WordPress.org|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2010-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101204003453/http://make.wordpress.org/ui/2010/05/20/yo-having-been-repeatedly-impressed-by/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Ghost的创始人John O'Nolan在博客里提出Ghost计划<ref>{{cite web|last=O'Nolan|first=John|title=Ghost: an idea for a new blogging platform|url=http://john.onolan.org/project-ghost/|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2019-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302022258/https://john.onolan.org/project-ghost/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，计划开发更简洁的[[博客|博客]]程序，而不是[[内容管理系统|内容管理系统]]。

2013年4月29日，O'Nolan为实施Ghost项目计划在[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]筹款£25,000<ref>{{cite web|title=Ghost: Just a Blogging Platform|url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/johnonolan/ghost-just-a-blogging-platform|publisher=Kickstarter|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204085945/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/johnonolan/ghost-just-a-blogging-platform|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而这个新项目在29天内获得£196,362筹款。<ref>{{cite web|last=Biggs|first=John|title=Ghost Will Take Your Boring Blog To The Next Astral Plane|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/05/07/ghost-will-take-your-boring-blog-to-the-next-astral-plane/|publisher=TechCrunch|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124010822/https://techcrunch.com/2013/05/07/ghost-will-take-your-boring-blog-to-the-next-astral-plane/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Warren|first=Christina|title=Is This Kickstarter Project the Future of Blogging?|url=http://mashable.com/2013/05/25/ghost-kickstarter-blogging/|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104221452/https://mashable.com/2013/05/25/ghost-kickstarter-blogging/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 成功获得了WooThemes，ENVATO和[[微软|微软]]公司的支持。

2013年9月19日， Ghost的第一个公开版本发布，预览版命名为Kerouac。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ghost 0.3 - Kerouac|url=http://blog.ghost.org/launch/|publisher=Ghost Foundation|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229170743/http://blog.ghost.org/launch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年10月14日， Ghost0.3.3在[[GitHub|GitHub]]发布。在GitHub进行开发、升级和更新。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ghost Repository - Github|url=http://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost|publisher=Github|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202102712/https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ghost Launches to The Public|url=http://blog.ghost.org/public-launch/|publisher=Ghost Foundation|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229172551/http://blog.ghost.org/public-launch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 管理組織 ==
Ghost 项目由位于新加坡的[[非营利组织|非营利组织]] Ghost Foundation 管理,<ref name="foundation">{{cite web |url=https://ghost.org/about/contact/ |title=The Ghost Foundation |accessdate=2014-12-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229171817/https://ghost.org/about/contact/ |archivedate=2014-12-29 }}</ref> 建立在 [[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]] 众筹基础上。 该基金会目前共有13名全职员工维护Ghost项目和在线社区基础设施。

== 商业模式 ==

Ghost博客软件可以免费下载和使用。 此外，Ghost 基金会提供了一个付费的博客托管平台，因此 Ghost Foundation 承担起安装、升级和維护服务器的工作。付费后, 用户能够完全掌控博客平台 享受自动备份、自动升级和邮件技术支持.<ref name="guardian-ghost">{{cite web | url = http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/sep/23/ghost-uk-blogging-platform-facebook | title = The Guardian - Ghost: the UK blogging platform that won't and can't sell out to Facebook | first = Alex | last = Fern | work = theguardian.com | accessdate = 15 December 2013 | date = 23 September 2013 | archive-date = 2019-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190425094203/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/sep/23/ghost-uk-blogging-platform-facebook | dead-url = no }}</ref> 于此同时，托管平台的收入会用于开发[[开源|开源]]软件和项目的维护<ref>{{cite web|last=Sawers|first=Paul|title=Open-source blogging platform Ghost begins rolling out its fully-hosted service|url=http://thenextweb.com/media/2013/12/16/open-source-blogging-platform-ghost/|publisher=The Next Web|accessdate=23 December 2013|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031082743/https://thenextweb.com/media/2013/12/16/open-source-blogging-platform-ghost/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

